Package com.tae.store.fragments

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BagFragment
    Fragment that implements the bag feature.
    CategoryFragment
    Fragment that implements a list with all the categories of the store.
    CustomMapFragment
    Map fragment where all the stores are displayed.
    HomeFragment
    Fragment that implements the home screen.
    ItemFragment
    Fragment where the product is display with more detail.
    LogInFragment
    Fragment where the user can register or login using a TAE or Facebook account.
    MyTaeFragment
    Fragment where the user can login and create an account or change his/her preferences, depending if the user is logged or no.
    NoConnectionFragment
    Fragment that alert to the user that the Internet connection is lost.
    PreferencesFragment
    Fragment where the suer can change some preferences.
    ProductListFragment
    Fragment where all the product of a category will be displayed.
    SlidePageFragment
    Fragment placed on the ViewPager.
    StoreFragment
    Fragment that show information about one store
    StoreListFragment
    Fragment that list all the stores in a range.
